reviews.review_text:
Shut....up! You won't learn much by reading this, but I thought it was funny.

After Bob says they are "making plans" some girl in the audience shouts "Shut....up!!!"

Bob deserves better, but it sounds hilarious. 

Pretty good show, good matrix too.
- Wow, what a brilliant show! One of my favorites of the year.

so spooky I don't know what it is about this show. Maybe the echo of the room on the AUD but this is my go-to show for May 1977. Estimated gives me chills, first IKO, one of the swingingest Berthas ever. The best AUDs allow you to enter this kind of mystical, spooky space, where the band, the crowd, the room, and the silence between the notes all come together. I wasn't here. I was only nine years old at the time. But listening to this puts me right there with all my brothers and sisters. Thank you.
